{"tid":1470024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼節燒衣 激光射何君堯","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:57:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf335fa7af0dfc8f25cabf9b2d54a68dc2b67437","tid":1470024,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190814/s00006/7a890c1f00439454ccb4efe67580e2f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190814%2Fs00006%2F7a890c1f00439454ccb4efe67580e2f8.jpg&h=92412005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】約30名屯門街坊昨晚趁盂蘭節前夕，到天后廟燒衣拜祭早前自殺的6名抗爭者，又以激光筆射向立法會議員何君堯的照片打算點火，但數十秒仍沒燒着，大叫「回水」。街坊其後改到屯門警署外聚集。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190814/s00001/1565721186016/%E9%AC%BC%E7%AF%80%E7%87%92%E8%A1%A3-%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%B0%84%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190814%2Fs00001%2F1565721186016%2F%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B0%2584%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=ebca99c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190814%2Fs00001%2F1565721186016%2F%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B0%2584%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF&h=a75ae897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190814/s00001/1565721186016/%E9%AC%BC%E7%AF%80%E7%87%92%E8%A1%A3-%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E5%B0%84%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF</a>"},{"pid":"082ce12479edb42fc72eaa7cfd0650ed497d9c59","tid":1470024,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08